            No prior experience required. We train you &mdash; Firefighter I, EMR, and
            driver/operator certifications are all available at no cost. You need to be 18
            (junior member at 16 with parental consent), live within a 10-minute drive of
            the station, and be able to commit to one drill night a month and calls as
            you're able.
          </p>
          <a href="mailto:chief@irafd.vt.gov?subject=Volunteer%20interest" class="btn"
            >Contact the Chief <span class="arr">&rarr;</span></a
          >
          <div class="req">Next recruit orientation &middot; May 20 &middot; 19:00</div>
